data.value:
Instructions:
Game Setup Controls: Right Bumber: Change Player Color
In Game Controls: Right Trigger: Shoot, Left Stick: Move, A: Jump
The object of Olah is for you to shoot at the other players. If you hit one of the other players they will be killed and respawn. If you are hit you will die and respawn. You can set the game's time limit in the Game Options menu. When the timer runs out, the player with the most kills wins.
